{["internalId"]="2558",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Margot Oscent has a son named Lucas who's missing, and she's worried he may have been taken by the slavers.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2556",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="A Knight of the Flame claims to have been put in the stocks unjustly. I need to convince the constable to release her.",["poiIndex"]="18",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2561",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="The Nurin family needs help. They awoke this morning to find their farm burning, overrun by dremora, and the father, William Nurin, is missing. I volunteered to help find him.",["poiIndex"]="15",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2578",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="The Supernal Dreamers have apparently built a few portals on the Nurin's farm through which they are summoning scamps and possibly other Daedra. I've agreed to destroy these portals.",["poiIndex"]="15",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2564",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Duchess Lakana needs someone to take a message to the leader of the Redguard camp outside the gates. Sir Hughes suggested I act as her messenger and report on what she reveals.",["poiIndex"]="17",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4146",["level"]="50",["type"]="5",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Survivors of the plague from Narsis have built a refugee camp inside long-abandoned crypts. Sela and her husband came to join the group, but became separated.",["poiIndex"]="20",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6041",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Razgurug requested I gather a magical substance from the runestones in Clockwork City. I'll also need to collect a special crystal that causes the residue to glow.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4151",["level"]="50",["type"]="5",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Sela does not believe Danus's story about Garil becoming infected. Something isn't right.",["poiIndex"]="20",["isShareable"]="1"},
