{["internalId"]="5588",["level"]="50",["type"]="3",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Spencer Rye runs a finder's business and uses the Thieves Guild to track down his quarries. Helping him will surely reflect well on your skill as a thief, and be lucrative to boot.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6356",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Nisuzi's Baandari clan needs oil from Darkpool Mine, but a flock of Mehrunes Dagon-worshipers took control of the cavernâ€”blocking access to the oil with hordes of newly summoned Daedra.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="5790",["level"]="50",["type"]="3",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Cardea Gallus of the Fighters Guild learned of Worm Cult activity in Shadowfen.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6288",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Several envoys from the Root-Whisper Village have gone missing, and Tuwul suspects that Blackguards are the ones responsible.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6078",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="After an argument with his sister Kireth concerning Raynor's behavior during the Shadow Crisis, the young artificer stormed off and vowed to finish exploring the Clockwork City on his own. Kireth asked me to go help him.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6192",["level"]="50",["type"]="6",["repeatType"]="1",["displayType"]="3",["backgroundText"]="Z'Maja, a powerful Sload sorceress, has filled the city of Cloudrest with an unnatural shadow which saps the life of all it touches. I've agreed to help Olorime defeat Z'Maja and save the city.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="0"},
{["internalId"]="6059",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Brengolin, the cook in Slag Town, needs some assistance in creating some unconventional cuisine and I have agreed to lend him a hand.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4086",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Aspera Giant-Friend says the giants are about to go to war against the Stormfists that hold Cradlecrush because their mammoths were stolen. As long as I oppose the Stormfists, these giants will consider me to be an ally.",["poiIndex"]="9",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4095",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Aspera and the giants are ready to begin the siege of Cradlecrush. Using the documents I recovered from the Stormfist scouts, they formulated a plan of battle.",["poiIndex"]="9",["isShareable"]="1"},
