{["internalId"]="5597",["level"]="50",["type"]="3",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Green-Venom-Tongue learned a few things from the Black Dragon's journal that seem to point to his former Sanctuary. He wants to go back there and try to confirm the Black Dragon's claims.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4902",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Shornhelm, the largest city in Rivenspire, is a city divided. House Montclair has annexed part of the city. Mollier Guillon suggested I go to Shornhelm and help Countess Tamrith deal with the situation.",["poiIndex"]="10",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6598",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I came across the body of Ansdurran. He apparently died after stealing a sacred relic of Hircine bound for a shrine in Markarth.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6563",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A strange and powerful storm disrupted the protective wards around the village of Karthwasten, turning a portion of its people feral. Apprentice Fialyn needs help restoring the wards.",["poiIndex"]="2",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6596",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I came across the body of Apprentice Gwerina. She apparently died while bringing a sacred relic to a shrine in Markarth.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6401",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A Dragon lairs on a nearby island, and Sai Sahan believes it plans to attack Senchal. I agreed to help Sai sail to the island and slay the beast before it can harm the city.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6407",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A gang of Alfiq thieves destroyed a priceless Khajiit tapestry and ran off with the pieces. I should find the pieces so that the masterpiece can be restored to its former glory.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="5598",["level"]="50",["type"]="3",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="The Black Hand has decreed that Lyra the Black Dragon must die for her crimes against the Brotherhood. Green-Venom-Tongue has gone to Knightsgrave to perform the task. Astara has asked me to back him up.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="5695",["level"]="50",["type"]="3",["repeatType"]="1",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I accepted one of the Dark Brotherhood's murder-for-hire contracts. There are no stipulations regarding methods or timing, so I may execute the target at my discretion.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="0"},
