{["internalId"]="5758",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Hermaeus Mora asked me to bring him unique relics from across Craglorn in exchange for knowledge of the Celestials.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6709",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found a notice that says House Hexos in Fargrave seeks adventurers for dangerous work.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6686",["level"]="50",["type"]="15",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="2",["backgroundText"]="Urgarlag Chief-bane of the Undaunted has challenged me to explore the Dread Cellar.",["poiIndex"]="67",["isShareable"]="0"},
{["internalId"]="6706",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found a page of a journal belonging to someone named Selveni. He says that he's on a mission to the False Martyrs' folly from the Tribunal.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6705",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found a note addressed to someone named Khazasha that talked about seeking revenge against a terrible beast called the Ravener. With her companions dead, she may need help.",["poiIndex"]="9",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6687",["level"]="50",["type"]="12",["repeatType"]="3",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="There are adventures to be had in the borderlands of Blackwood, in the southeastern region of Cyrodiil. Seek out Chanil-Jei near the Impresario's camp for more information.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6744",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I encountered Valsirenn trapped in a sychroseisiac state, out of phase with reality and in need of assistance. She asked me to help her locate a sage named Master Rrvenk, who is supposed to be a master of the Eleventh Force: Change.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6721",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Dagonists drugged Saraathu Tong operativesâ€”along with other prisonersâ€”and left them outside Taupezu Azzida's lair to be eaten. I need to give the prisoners the antidote and kill Taupezu Azzida before it's too late.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6707",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="We destroyed an Incarnate at Burning Gyre Keep, but Lyranth believes that the Waking Flame plans to create more. She wants to find the Riven Cataclyst before they doâ€”and she thinks the Bladebearer Dremora can point us to our goal.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6708",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="The mad prisoner Elegian, creator of the Riven Cataclyst, told me we can get to the device by going to Annihilarch's Summit. I need to locate the cataclyst before Sister Celdina unleashes more Incarnates to attack Fargrave and Nirn.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6699",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="We destroyed the Riven Cataclyst at Fort Grief, but Sister Celdina escaped. We believe she retreated to a hidden stronghold in a forgotten realm known as Deadlight. We need to find this realm and deal with the cult once and for all.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6700",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="We defeated Sister Celdina, but Valkynaz Nokvroz captured the Anchorite. He wants to use her blood as fuel for his own cataclyst device. Lyranth thinks Nokvroz is holding her in his fortress, Ardent Hope. We need to rescue her.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6696",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Lyranth thinks we need to find the Fourth Ambition and gather up Sombren and Calia before Mehrunes Dagon goes after them and launches his next plot to conquer Nirn. She has once again asked me to help her.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6697",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Sombren decided to join Mehrunes Dagon. He stole Calia's power and added it to his own. Now we must protect the Anchorite and figure out how to find and use the egonymic if we hope to defeat Sombren and Mehrunes Dagon.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6693",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Mehrunes Dagon has been defeated and his plot to take over Tamriel has been thwarted. Eveli thinks we need to check in with our allies and rendezvous in Leyawiin.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2777",["level"]="50",["type"]="7",["repeatType"]="1",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I accepted a mission to scout Blue Road Keep for the Covenant.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="0"},
{["internalId"]="6723",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Lyranth the Dremora sent me a letter. She wants me to meet her in Fargrave, a city somewhere in the depths of Oblivion. Apparently, the Order of the Waking Flame is up to something that threatens both Fargrave and Nirn.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6731",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I came across the body of a Redguard. It looks like he was in the middle of delivering something to Nass in the House of Whims in Fargrave.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6738",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="The legendary mage, Divayth Fyr, came to Fargrave in search of a powerful Daedric artifact called the Ebony Blade. However, the owners hid it away under mysterious circumstances. I agreed to help Divayth uncover the truth of the missing sword.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6724",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="Our only clue as to the next step in Sister Celdina and the Waking Flame's plans is an encoded note we can't decipher. Both Lyranth and the Anchorite believe that we can find someone in Fargrave who can translate it for us.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6694",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Tephilaz, a Daedra living in Wretched Spire, died suddenly on the street. The locals suspect someone murdered him to stop a treaty. A Dremora named Noroth seeks the killer before more violence erupts.",["poiIndex"]="16",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6727",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A member of the Grasp named Zyr asked me to help track down a group of thieves who stole a large quantity of Redmaiden from Fargrave. Apparently, they fled to the Sever after leaving Fargrave.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6698",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found a letter on a dead member of the Order of the Waking Flame cult. The letter describes a place called the Brandfire Reformatory, where the cult brainwashes their unwilling recruits. I should find the Brandfire Reformatory and investigate.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6729",["level"]="50",["type"]="12",["repeatType"]="3",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A Wood Elf writer named Calonir needs help conducting research for his travel brochure. If I can provide some information on the hazards and highlights of Vvardenfell, Summerset, and lands beyond, I can earn a bit of gold for my trouble.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="0"},
{["internalId"]="4669",["level"]="33",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="1",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I'm now participating in Spikeball, a foot race where I can throw a Spikeball to stun opponents.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="4816",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="10",["backgroundText"]="A villager from Tava's Blessing asked that I seek out a Thronekeeper named Luala al-Tava.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="3187",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A Khajiit named Ildani was apparently caught trying to smuggle her wares into Sentinel. She's asked me to help her recover the confiscated goods.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6695",["level"]="50",["type"]="12",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="4",["backgroundText"]="Witchmother Taerma asked for my help to defeat a Wraith-of-Crows from the Evergloam called the Crowborne Horror. She tasked me with collecting feathers from vile creatures in order to form an effigy that can bring the creature forth.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6718",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="The Unmaker presents a challenge to even the strongest Daedra, so many try to test their might against it and fail. Vaveli Indavel hired me to kill the Unmaker, as well as the Havocrel around it, and bring back armor for the Saraathu Tong.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6712",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Luna Beriel has witness accounts of some valuables lying in the False Martyrs' Folly from when the Martyrs there were turned to stone. She wants me to go to the Folly and bring the items back.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6713",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Luna Beriel tasked me with going into the False Martyrs' Folly to retrieve some martyrs' copperleaf plants for Tuleenith, a healer in Fargrave.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6719",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Taupezu Azzida, a Mantikora in the Sever, poisons its prey. The Saraathu Tong wants to study the Mantikora's victims to make an antidote out of the venom. They want the Mantikora killed so no one can use the venom to harm mortals.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6711",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Luna Beriel tasked me with recovering relics from the Brandfire Reformatory, a fearsome building in the Deadlands where the Waking Flame cult takes prisoners and doesn't release them.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6717",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Vaveli Indavel asked me to place seeing stones around the den of the Unmaker and kill the creature on the behalf of Vares Dredayn, who is studying the creature's death cycle.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6715",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Luna Beriel says a Gleaner operative left a shipment of goods at three drop sites in the Shambles, but they haven't been picked up yet. If those goods are left in the Shambles too long, they'll be stolen.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6728",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found the body of a Scamp alongside a note and bag in the Deadlands.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6730",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I found the body of a Spiderkith, Telofasa. It looks like she died while attempting to deliver something.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6710",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A merchant named Fyna commissioned Luna Beriel and the Gleaners of Arubis to sneak into the Brandfire Refomatory and destroy the propaganda the Order of the Waking Flame is making there.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6716",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="An Infernium called the Unmaker and multiple Havocrels wiped out a Daedric merchant caravan. Vaveli Indavel asked me to kill the monsters and bring back some of the lost supplies.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6714",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Luna Beriel gave me some papers containing important information from the Gleaners founder, Pieron Desant. The letters need to be dropped in letterboxes throughout the Blood Pit for the Gleaners' agents imprisoned there.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6720",["level"]="50",["type"]="1",["repeatType"]="2",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="A previous group of heroes left the Saraathu Tong's liminal rods in a Mantikora's lair. Vaveli Indavel tasked me with destroying the rods and killing Taupezu Azzida, the Mantikora.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="6732",["level"]="50",["type"]="0",["repeatType"]="0",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="Nass told me that the planestones I brought to her open a portal to the hidden and valuable treasure of Uxark, a Xivilai warrior.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="1"},
{["internalId"]="2733",["level"]="50",["type"]="7",["repeatType"]="1",["displayType"]="0",["backgroundText"]="I accepted a mission to scout Drakelowe Farm for the Dominion.",["poiIndex"]="294967291",["isShareable"]="0"},
